  "message": "Update benchmarks with complete 5-runtime comparison\n\n- Use fib(25)\u00d75 instead of fib(35)\u00d7100 so wasmedge-qjs completes\n- Add complete data for all 5 runtimes (EdgeBox, Bun, wasmedge-qjs, Node.js, Porffor)\n- Add transparency note about bytecode caching vs raw JS interpretation",
